1. Ja *saznajem* nove informacije svakog dana. (I learn new information every day.)
2. Oni *saznaju* istinu o svojoj prošlosti. (They discover the truth about their past.)
3. Kada ćeš *saznati* rezultate ispita? (When will you find out the results of the exam?)
4. Da li su novinari *saznali* detalje o incidentu? (Did the journalists find out details about the incident?)
5. Oni su *saznali* da je konkurencija veoma jaka. (They found out that the competition is very strong.)
6. Neki ljudi vole da *saznaju* sve o drugima. (Some people like to find out everything about others.)
7. Bilo je teško *saznati* pravi uzrok problema. (It was difficult to discover the real cause of the problem.)
8. Kako su *saznali* gde se nalazi tajna baza? (How did they find out where the secret base is?)
9. Nadam se da ćemo *saznati* više o tome sutra. (I hope we'll find out more about it tomorrow.)
10. Možemo li *saznati* više o vašem projektu? (Can we learn more about your project?)

Note: In all of these sentences, the word "saznaju" (or a conjugated form of the word) is highlighted with a star (*).